  <data key="d4">"The floor for the Global Diversified Index Account."&lt;SEP&gt;"The floor for the NASDAQ-100 Index Account."&lt;SEP&gt;"The floor that protects the account from negative interest, ensuring no loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"The interest credited when the index declines, protected by the floor."&lt;SEP&gt;"The minimum interest rate guaranteed to be credited to the index account."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8c5042e90fe6248acf672391208bb506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29c4478dd9be0cdf43be914d5e56c59f</data>
